lifeSkillSource.Name: Luna Ore
lifeSkillSource.Des: Low-grade Luna ore is commonly found near the Scout Lookout Post. While focused on gathering, you may harvest Luna Ore, which is used to craft Fine Forgestone.

SpecialAward.Des: 10% chance to gain 1 extra item when gathering with focus.

SpecialAward.Name: Mining Yielding Pro
SpecialAward.Des: 20% chance to gain 1 extra item when gathering with focus.

SpecialAward.Name: Mining Yielding Master
SpecialAward.Des: 30% chance to gain 1 extra item when gathering with focus.
